  "description": "Blocked reason: src/agent_takt/tui/app.py TuiSchedulerReporter.bead_deferred() (lines 1099-1102): state.deferred_this_cycle is assigned before _post() is called. If this is the first reporter call in a cycle, _post() clears the just-assigned set via .clear(), silently dropping the deferred bead ID. Fix: reorder to call _post() first, then update _deferred_this_cycle and sync to state. Add a test covering the first-call-in-cycle edge case.\n\nRemaining work: Fix the bead_deferred() ordering bug: move _post() call before the deferred_this_cycle state sync to prevent _post()'s cycle-start clear from erasing the just-written bead ID.",
